OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNHS could give therapy     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbefore anti-depressants,   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Funder new guidelines       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, People in England with mild depression 
OL,6, should first be offered behavioural    
OL,7, therapy or group exercise instead of   
OL,8, medication, according to new advice.   
OL,10,FThe clinical watchdog also recommends  
OL,11,Fmindfulness and meditation as possible 
OL,12,Falternatives to anti-depressants in new
OL,13,Fguidelines under consultation.         
OL,15,FAnti-depressant use has increased in   
OL,16,Frecent years - with an estimated one in
OL,17,Fseven people in England taking them.   
OL,19,FMore than 20 million were prescribed in
OL,20,Fjust three months last year.           
